Rulings.Base: 1. If the monsters that destroyed your opponent's monsters by battle are no longer on the field, this card will still be able to attack twice.\n2. If your monsters destroy 2 or more of your opponent's monsters by battle and then "Rhinotaurus" is Special Summoned during that same Battle Phase, it can attack twice.\n3. If your monsters destroy 2 or more of your opponent's monsters by battle and you take control of your opponent's "Rhinotaurus" during that Battle Phase, it can attack twice.
